china 's export of high - tech products in first two months of 1996
xinhua news agency , guangzhou , march 16 , ( reporter chen ji ) the latest statistics show that from january to february this year , the export of high - tech products in guangdong province reached $ 37.6 billion , an increase of 34.8 percent over the same period last year , accounting for 25.5 percent of the province 's total export volume .
the frequent export of high - tech products has made important contributions to the growth of guangdong 's foreign trade .
last year , the export of high - tech products in guangdong province was 229.4 billion us dollars , up 31% over the same period last year , and the growth rate was 27.2 percent higher than that of the whole province . the net export of high - tech products increased by 52.7 billion us dollars , making up for the decrease in the export value of traditional labor - intensive products .
among the export of new high level technology products in guangdong , computer and communications technology products were unique , and last year , the export volume was 1.194 billion us dollars , accounting for 85.9 percent of the total export value of new high level technology products in the whole province .
the main market for export of high - tech products in guangdong province is hong kong , the united states , the european union , and japan .
last year , the export of new high level technology industrial belts in the pearl river delta reached $ 219.9 billion , accounting for 98.7 percent of the province 's total export volume of high - tech products .
this year , such a leading role is still very prominent .
at present , over 95 percent of the computers in the pearl river delta region are capable of providing all computer spare parts in the field of the azimuth .
