the fifa executive committee also announced some reform measures .
in order to allow the players to get rid of the ball , the prerequisite is that they cannot affect the normal competition , and as some players , the international football association has made it easy for them to have some contradictions in the minds of the game , and from 1 july this year , it is not necessary to write any words on the back of the game of the world cup players , but it is necessary to be in the front of the sports .
suicide bombing in jerusalem
xinhua news agency report of march 17 from jerusalem ( by staff reporter zhong huihua and nie xiaoyang ) a man , who was carrying a bomb in a residential area in northern jerusalem on the afternoon of the 17 th , was killed and nine other people were slightly injured and sent to the hospital for treatment .
at present , the police have sealed off the scene of the explosion .
in less than two hours ago , a palestinian gunshot occurred in the northern israeli town of karabi .
according to the latest report , a 16 - year - old israeli girl was killed and at least 12 others were injured .
the gunman was shot to death by the police .
so far , no organization has claimed responsibility for the attack .
the israeli prime minister 's office condemned the shooting .
israeli prime minister sharon said on the same day that although israel and the palestinian side are making a cease - fire effort , the israeli side will respond to any attack .
