xinhua news agency , hangzhou , march 18 , this year is the fifth anniversary of the return of hong kong to the motherland , and the first chinese civil service 's " regulations on the conduct of civil servants " will be promulgated and implemented to celebrate the two happy events , and a civil service painting competition with the theme of " state civil servants - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - the people civil servants " - - - - - - - - will be launched in hong kong , macao , and the mainland civil servants .
