the french delegation , who took part in the eighth paralympic games in salt lake city in the united states , won 19 medals at the 8 th national games , including nine gold medals , one gold medal , and 10 medals including one gold medal .
this is the best result of the french delegation in the winter olympic games .
at the welcoming ceremony , the french athletes said that their special performance has changed their views on them , and the french people are grateful for their outstanding contributions in the struggle to change their views on the disabled .
the minister said in his speech that the french government will , as always , continue to support the disabled sports movement .
