xinhua news agency , kiev , march 22 ( reporter zhang zhiqiang ) ukrainian president kuchma gave a speech to the press on the 22 nd on the us house of representatives ' interference in the internal affairs of ukraine , saying that the resolution of the us house of representatives was an unprecedented incident and " incomprehensible " .
the us house of representatives adopted a resolution on the upcoming election of the ukrainian parliament , calling on ukraine to hold a transparent , free and fair election on the 31 st of this month .
the resolution also pointed out that the ukrainian government should earnestly implement the new parliament election law , and the election results should indicate whether ukraine will continue to carry out democratic reforms .
kuchma said : " the ukrainian nation is not a football that can be made at will , and the ukrainian people should have their own dignity . "
kuchma also thanked the president of the world 's ubrzezinski for his letter to the united states .
in his letter , brzezinski said : " look at what you have done .
we have studied well at home and then taught others . "
on the same day , the ukrainian leader said that the us act was a gross interference in ukraine 's internal affairs and a threat to ukraine 's independence .
the u.s. house of representatives ' one - sided evaluation of ukraine 's election campaign will lead to the separation of the political forces in the country , the official said .
a spokesman for the ukrainian foreign ministry said today that the election of the supreme legislative organ and the representatives of the local legislative organs is purely a matter of the ukrainian people .
in the final stage of the election campaign in the ukrainian parliament , it is hoped that all countries will show a cautious attitude and will abide by the norms of international law that do not interfere in their internal affairs .
