the french philadelphia is the first non - russian astronauts to fly to the space station , and he will carry out two space flights when the mission starts .
the shell group 's investment in china will reach 5 billion us dollars in three years
xinhua news agency , beijing , march 26 ( reporter qian chunpei ) - the chairman of the board of directors of the shell - producing group , wu jichuan , said a few days ago that by 2005 , the total investment of the shell group in china will reach 5 billion us dollars .
at the china development forum held here , he said : currently , shell 's investment in china has reached 1.6 billion us dollars , plus some of the ongoing projects , with a total investment of 5 billion us dollars in 2005 .
shell is currently negotiating many cooperative projects with the chinese side .
among them , 500 gas stations are expected to be set up in jiangsu province this year .
he said that shell 's business contacts with china have been more than 100 years .
for shell , china 's market has huge potential and is an important part of its global strategy .
as the economy develops , china 's demand for energy is expected to double the consumption of energy by 2020 , which will account for 16 percent of the world 's total .
china is facing severe energy challenges , and the diversification of energy sources is very important for energy safety and environmental protection , and the shell card will play an important role in this process .
