xinhua news agency , tokyo , march 29 , japanese foreign minister chuan leekpai announced on the 29 th that japan will temporarily freeze its humanitarian aid to russia until the japanese side will carry out rectification and reform of the international committee responsible for the aid project .
the japanese government will control the japanese government 's financial assistance to russia in addition to maintaining the commission 's human expenditure and japan 's existing technical cooperation projects .
the move was made in response to a recent remark made by japanese finance minister yanchuan zhengchuan leekpai .
yanchuan zhengchuan leekpai recently proposed to the cabinet members that , in view of the continued worsening of the financial situation in japan , the cabinet members should ensure that each of the government 's funds can be used .
it has been learned that after being exposed by the deputy chief executive of the cabinet , suzuki , the deputy chief executive of the ministry of foreign affairs , has been criticized by the outside world for the malfeasance of the application procedures of the russian aid project and the lack of transparency on the issue of funds .
eu to hold consultations with china on implementation of temporary safeguard measures for steel imports
xinhua news agency , beijing , march 29 ( reporter shi guangsheng ) - chinese minister of foreign trade and economic cooperation shi guangsheng said here today that the eu has made a clear response to the eu 's temporary safeguard measures for the implementation of some imported steel , and that it will hold consultations with the chinese side as soon as possible and make some special arrangements for china as a developing country .
today , shi guangsheng answered a reporter 's question at the national conference on legal work in foreign trade and economic cooperation .
he said : at present , the more and more advanced the iron and steel trade war is , the source is from the united states .
at present , all parties concerned have put forward demands on the us " 201 steel case " and bilateral consultations , and some have even put forward a mechanism to resolve the issue through the wto disputes .
on 27 march , the eu decided to promptly respond to the temporary safeguard measures for the import of 15 kinds of steel from various countries , and shi guangsheng sent a letter to eu trade commissioner lamy , expressing deep concern over this and put forward bilateral negotiations with the eu .
seven killed in train collision in liaoning province
xinhua news agency , shenyang , march 30 ( reporter wang jun ) a train collision accident occurred in jinzhou city , liaoning province , at 14 : 13 on the 29 th , killing seven people and injuring three .
according to the safety inspection office of the shenyang railway bureau , a four - wheel agricultural vehicle collided with a train from the jinzhou county to the zhou jianyan district in the case of the accident .
at that time , 50 bags of chemical fertilizers and seeds were erected on the vehicle , and 14 people were also violated the regulations .
during the collision , four people were killed and no injuries were injured , and the remaining 10 people were injured , and the train compartments were damaged to a certain extent .
after the accident , leaders of the ministry of railways , the shenyang railway bureau , and the jinzhou city government have rushed to the scene to deal with the aftermath of the accident .
the council of arab states held an emergency meeting at the arab league headquarters on the same day to discuss the palestinian situation .
representatives of 22 arab countries ' permanent arab league attended the meeting .
at a press conference after the meeting , moussa said that israel 's military action against palestine clearly indicated that israel refused to accept peace .
what is currently taking place is israel 's continuation of its military occupation over palestine , and the palestinian people will continue to resist israel 's aggression .
he said : " as long as israel occupies the palestinian territory one day , as long as the tanks and soldiers of israel exist in the palestinian territory , the palestinian people 's resistance will continue for one day . "
