on the afternoon of the same day , israeli prime minister sharon held a meeting at the core to discuss the current situation between israel and palestine and how to cope with the increasingly frequent bombing attacks on the palestinian side , and the meeting decided to increase military strikes against the palestinian side .
people in the political circles here have revealed that the security cabinet holds that increasing the intensity of the palestinian attacks can weaken the momentum of terrorist activities , but it is impossible to fundamentally stop such attacks .
