in a televised speech to the whole country , chavez thanked the venezuelan people for their trust and support for him , thanked the organization of the american states , the rio group , and the group of 77 and other international organizations for their actions to safeguard democracy and condemn the coup d ' etat , and called on all circles in venezuela to take a reconcile action .
chavez stressed that venezuela needs peace , stability , and wisdom , and that all sides should make joint efforts to stop the conflict .
he said : through this incident , " we have learned many things , and we will strive to correct the mistakes and errors in the past and build our country together . "
a military coup took place on the 11 th in venezuela , and more than 10 high - ranking officers declared that they would not support the chavez administration and would be detained by chavez .
carmona , former chairman of the venezuelan business council , was appointed as interim president of the transitional government on the 12 th .
on the same day , the masses in support of chavez held a peaceful demonstration in the capital , asking chavez to retake office .
on the afternoon of the 13 th , a group of relatives and friends , the vice president for the protection of the military personnel , returned to the presidential palace , and was sworn in as the interim president , carmona announced his resignation .
the armed forces supporting chavez then issued an ultimatum to the coup military , and occupied the important strategic stronghold army .
in the early morning of 14 april , chavez returned to the presidential palace by helicopter from the detained caribbean island .
xinhua news agency , damascus , april 15 ( reporter ren zhenxi ) syrian president basins held talks with visiting us secretary of state colin powell here on the 15 th , during which the two sides discussed the latest development of the middle east situation , especially the serious situation in palestine , and the tense situation in the lebanon - israel border region .
according to a report from the syrian news agency , president bashar said during the talks : " the incident in palestine has caused the ( middle east ) peace process to enter a dead - end street . if we cannot understand this point , the development of the matter may reach the level of recovery . at that time , we can only wait for the time of the generation . "
he pointed out that only after israel withdraws from the palestinian territories occupied by it can it talk about the peace process .
he said : " only when both sides are willing to realize peace can peace be realized . "
he called on the united states to have clear - cut views on middle east peace and play a role in this regard so that relevant un resolutions can be effectively implemented .
with regard to the suicide act carried out by the palestinians , bashar said that these actions are not the root cause of the current incident in the occupied palestinian territories , but the consequences of the incident , and are counterattacks against israel .
he pointed out : the best way to do so is to remove the tension in palestine .
according to diplomatic sources , during the talks between powell and bashar , they also discussed the issue of the border between lebanon and israel .
powell arrived in syria at noon that day for a short visit from beirut .
new york stock market moves lower
xinhua news agency , new york , april 15 , the dow jones index dropped to the lowest level in eight weeks due to the poor performance of the citibank and the mainland airlines .
the dow jones industrial average closed down 97.15 at 10,93.67 , the lowest level since february 22 , and the technology heavy nasdaq composite index fell 2.41 at 173.78 , and the standard & amp ;
the nyse composite index and the russell 2000 index of smaller companies fell 0.23 at 438.45 and the american stock exchange composite index rose slightly .
nyse volume declined to 1.62 billion shares from 12.6 billion in the previous session .
the citibank announced on the same day that due to the loss of business in argentina , the bank 's first quarter profit did not achieve its expected target , and the mainland airlines also announced that the first quarter of this year was a loss .
as a result , investors are worried about the achievements of listed companies to be announced this week , so they have maintained a wait - and - see attitude .
wall street stocks fell to a low level after the slight fluctuations in the wall street and the volume of trading was also lower .
the technologies of the citibank , the mainland 's aviation , general electric , and other blue chips , such as microsoft , intel , the intel corp . , the orthodox , the dome , and the sun , all fell .
powell to hold talks with palestinian and israeli leaders again
xinhua news agency , jerusalem , april 16 ( reporter zhong chui - hua ) us secretary of state colin powell , who is visiting here , will hold talks with israeli prime minister sharon and palestinian national authority chairman arafat on the afternoon of the 16 th and 17 th .
according to reports , powell will postpone his visit to the middle east for at least 24 hours and continue to mediate between israel and palestine .
powell expressed the hope that israel and palestine will issue a joint statement , condemning the terrorist attacks on israelis and palestinians , and calling for the establishment of a palestinian state through negotiations and continuing to crack down on terrorism .
on the evening of 15 july , powell concluded his one - day visit to lebanon and syria , and returned to israel , and announced the plan to hold talks with arafat on 16 july .
powell told the press that the united states supports sharon 's proposal on holding regional and regional meetings , and also said that arafat could send a high - level delegation to attend the meeting .
in this regard , arafat has indicated that only israel will immediately withdraw its troops from the west bank control area , and that the palestinian side will accept the proposal of holding regional peace and stability .
powell held talks with sharon on 12 june .
on 14 july , he went to ramallah , the west bank city of the jordan river to hold talks with ' arafat , who was surrounded by israeli troops .
on the evening of the same day , he briefed sharon on the situation of the talks with arafat .
u.n. high commissioner for refugees visits afghanistan
xinhua news agency , kabul , april 16 ( reporter liu xuqian ) - the un high commissioner for refugees , who is currently on a visit to afghanistan , met with afghan interim government chairman karzai on the evening of the 15 th , and the two sides held talks on the return of the refugees to the countryside and the reintegration of the society .
the united nations , the unhcr , said in a press release on the 16 th that the reintegration of refugees into the society is important to the realization of stability in afghanistan .
he stressed that the security problem of refugees returning to the countryside must be protected , and the security of the rural areas is very important to avoiding the excessive influx of refugees into the cities .
karzai thanked the unhcr for its long - term work in afghanistan .
he said that reintegration of refugees into society is one of the key tasks of the interim government .
he stressed that the return of those who have lost their homes in the country is an urgent problem that has to be resolved .
he said that the current situation in most areas of afghanistan is stable , and there are sufficient rainwater , and that these people can immediately resume farming and be self - reliant on grain after returning to their native place .
according to a spokesman for the united nations refugee office , since the un refugee office and the afghan interim government officially started to help the refugees return to their home country on march 1 , more than 240,000 afghan refugees have returned from pakistan , and the number of refugees returned from iran has reached 5,000 , and the remaining 4,000 from tajikistan has returned to the country .
forty per cent of these people had flowed into the city .
miers arrived in afghanistan after concluding their visit to iran .
he will visit pakistan on 17 july .
