putin 's state of the nation address
xinhua news agency , moscow , april 18 , russian president putin issued a state of the nation address at the joint meeting of the russian parliament on the 18 th , pointing out that russia should become a powerful and competitive country , and should work hard to develop a constructive and normal relationship with all countries in the world , and should become a real member of the international community .
putin said : russia 's national construction goal is still to develop democracy and build a civilized market economy , and the most important thing is to improve the people 's living standards .
in summing up last year 's work , he pointed out that the country has achieved certain results in fulfilling its main tasks , the economy has maintained a sustained growth , the number of unemployed people has decreased , the people 's living standards have improved , and the russian people are full of confidence in the future .
putin expressed satisfaction with the good implementation of the budget and the improvement of the operating environment for two years running .
he stressed in particular that russia 's oil output has already ranked second in the world , and its energy trade volume ranks first in the world .
in his state of the nation address , putin also expounded the national development plan and domestic and foreign policies for this year .
this was the third time that putin issued a state of the nation address to the two chambers of the parliament since he took office as president .
nearly 1,000 members , 89 main federal leaders , the president 's office , and the responsible persons of government departments attended the joint meeting .
china supports european parliament 's report
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 19 , in response to a reporter 's question today , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue commented on a report passed by the european parliament .
a reporter asked : on 11 april , the plenary session of the european parliament deliberated and adopted the " report on the european parliament 's strategic documents on china . "
what is china 's comment on this ?
zhang qiyue answered : the chinese side has noticed that the european parliament has recently passed this report .
the report held that china and the eu have a wide range of common interests , advocate the development of sino - eu partnership , strengthen bilateral contacts , exchanges , and dialogue , and expand cooperation in the economic , trade , science and technology , education , culture , and other fields .
we welcome the above - mentioned positive proposals .
however , the report has made many wrong conclusions on china 's human rights situation , taiwan , and tibet issues , and seriously interfered in china 's internal affairs . this is unacceptable to the chinese side .
it is hoped that the european parliament will earnestly abide by the one - china principle and do more things beneficial to the development of bilateral relations , so as to avoid creating a negative impact on sino - european relations .
