xinhua news agency , shijiazhuang , april 20 ( reporter yan jie ) the reporter learned from the hebei provincial department of foreign trade and economic cooperation that since the beginning of this year , nearly 200 enterprises of various types have handled the registration rights of foreign trade and economic cooperation in the provincial foreign trade and economic cooperation department , which is 2.3 times that of the same period last year .
according to sources , there are 39 registered foreign trade companies , including 17 private foreign trade companies .
there are also dozens of commercial , material , and marketing enterprises and state - owned collective enterprises .
the number of private production enterprises also announced the right to manage foreign trade .
more and more private enterprises have joined the wto , which is a new atmosphere in which they declare their foreign trade right now .
in july last year , the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation further relaxed the conditions and standards for the import and export management rights of all types of enterprises , and changed the original examination and approval and registration system to a unified standard and management method for various types of ownership enterprises , thus promoting the enthusiasm of all types of enterprises in the declaration .
