xinhua news agency , beijing , april 21 , chinese foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue pointed out here today that the chinese side resolutely opposes the japanese leader 's visit to the yasukuni shrine , which is enshrined in the spirits of class - a war criminals in any form .
the chinese side expressed strong dissatisfaction with the action of the japanese leader .
commenting on japanese prime minister junichiro koizumi 's visit to the yasukuni shrine this morning , zhang qiyue said that the japanese way of doing so will only damage japan 's own image and make it more difficult for japan to win the trust of the people of all asian countries on the issue of history .
this is koizumi 's second visit to the yasukuni shrine since he took office .
the yasukuni shrine is a place where the japanese pay respects to war criminals who died in the war of aggression since the meiji restoration , and the hideki tojo and other class - a war criminals who died in the war of aggression are also enshrined here .
france holds first round of voting in presidential election
xinhua news agency , paris , april 21 ( reporter liang guihe and the first round of voting for the french presidential election began at 840,000 polling stations in france on the morning of the 21 st .
of the 16 candidates , 40 million will be elected as the seventh president of the republic of france .
the result was announced later on the day .
according to the french ministry of interior , the voter turnout rate was 21.41 percent at noon on the 21 st , which was lower than the figure of 22.52 percent in the first round of the presidential election in 1995 .
according to the media here , this year 's voter turnout rate may hit the lowest level in history .
the french constitution stipulates that if no candidate wins more than 51 percent of the votes in the first round of voting , then the two candidates will enter the second round of the may 5 election .
according to the final opinion poll released last friday , incumbent president chirac and incumbent prime minister lionel jospin may win a very close vote in the first round .
since the number of candidates in the presidential election has reached a record high in france , the number of voters may be very scattered in the first round of voting .
in the first round of the election , the presidential candidate of the french ultra - rightist national front may occupy the third place , and may even get into the " cold door " of the former two .
