npc deputies still dissatisfied with judicial system reform achievements
( zhou yupeng report ) more than one - fourth of the npc deputies yesterday voted against the work report of the supreme people 's court and the supreme people 's procuratorate , indicating that they are still dissatisfied with the reform achievements of the judicial system and the progress of the rule of law .
however , at the great hall of the people , 2813 deputies attending the closing session of the fifth session of the ninth national people 's congress [ npc ] , 2742 people voted for premier zhu rongji 's government work report , and the rate of the approval rate was 97.5 percent , which was similar to last year .
all sides expect that zhu rongji , who has openly indicated that he will withdraw from the standing committee of the political bureau of the cpc 's 16 th cpc national congress , which will be held this fall .
however , the result of the vote showed that zhu was not cold by the npc deputies due to the imminent loss of power .
the 10 - and - a - half - day congress yesterday also approved a deficit of 309.8 billion yuan ( about 8.68 billion yuan ) for 2002 .
li peng , chairman of the standing committee of the national people 's congress , made a report on the work of the npc standing committee , which was slightly more than last year 's opposition to and abstentions .
the report of the standing committee of the national people 's congress [ npc ] yesterday won a vote of no . 7 votes , 112 against , and 114 abstentions .
last year 's report won 472 votes , 85 votes , and 122 abstentions .
although the response of the npc deputies yesterday was slightly better than last year , the npc deputies still voted against the work report of the supreme people 's court and the supreme people 's procuratorate .
xiao yang , president of the supreme people 's court , received 2026 votes , 528 votes , and 259 abstentions yesterday .
last year , his report received 193 votes , 530 votes , and 306 abstentions .
the report of han zhubin , procurator general of the supreme people 's procuratorate , received 2044 votes , 516 against , and 253 abstentions yesterday .
last year , his report received 1873 votes , 584 votes , and 332 abstentions .
since this year is the last session of the current npc , the npc will be changed to the next year . therefore , the " decision on the election of the 10 th national people 's congress [ npc ] , " which is to be adopted by yesterday , has been stipulated that the 10 th npc should be elected by the end of january next year .
china to accelerate change of local party and government leaders
a source in beijing 's " two sessions " revealed to ming pao that after the conclusion of the national people 's congress [ npc ] and the national committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference [ cppcc ] , the work of the local party and government leaders will be accelerated .
the central authorities demanded that all localities carry out the work of electing new leading bodies before the end of june this year , and the 17 provinces , municipalities , and autonomous regions that have yet to be completed will form new leading bodies .
the report said : according to the cpc central committee 's selection and appointment standards , members of provincial - level party and government leading bodies should generally have college - level or higher education level or above .
the central authorities also stipulate that the new secretary of the provincial party committee is under 59 years of age and under 56 years of age .
in addition , in order to strengthen the cpc 's leadership over people 's congresses at all levels , the people 's congresses at all levels will be given the position of party committees at the same level .
sources pointed out that since march last year , 62 party and government leaders in 31 provinces , autonomous regions , and municipalities across the country have been transferred and replaced .
among them , since last year , a total of 14 provinces and municipalities have completed the adjustment of local party committees , including inner mongolia , jiangxi , hubei , hainan , yunnan , and qinghai .
in various provinces , municipalities , and autonomous regions , the provincial governors and mayors of shanghai , jiangxi , shandong , hunan , and yunnan , totaling 11 provincial and ministerial - level officials were transferred to the posts .
