( seoul , us - us joint venture ) south korean officials said that a north korean patrol boat intruded into south korea 's territorial waters yesterday .
the south korean navy ship , which crossed the yellow sea 15 - km border and stayed 42 minutes later , was driven by south korean warships .
it said that the dprk patrol boat was carrying out an inspection of a cambodian ship intruding into south korea 's territorial waters .
obviously , the sea border between south korea and north korea is not clear , and yesterday 's situation was the second time in this year 's time .
the rok accused the dprk of violating 12 sea areas in the western region last year , but every time it was not serious .
in 1999 , a series of korean naval incidents caused the first sea clash since the korean war , causing a north korean naval vessel to sink , and it was believed that 30 north korean soldiers were killed .
