( washington , d . c . ) according to a us media report , a us official who was unwilling to reveal his name said recently that in the past few weeks , the international number one terrorist group , the al - qaeda , which has increased its financial activities . this shows that some leaders of the al - qaeda organization are resuming their control over the organization and may seek more financial assistance to the united states .
the official said that while the fund flow in the al - qaeda was increasing , the communication link between the survivors was also increasing .
