( auckland ) an expert of the us national ice and snow data center said yesterday that a ice in the antarctic has been completely disintegrated and split into several thousand ice mountains , which is the largest in the past 30 years , and the issue of global climate warming has been issued again .
it has been learned that the b - ice - b ice , with a total area of 3250 square kilometers , has been completely disintegrated after 35 days of time .
the center warned that with the coming of the hot summer , other ice cap was also on the brink of collapse .
this indicates that the glaciers in the south polar sea will increase , and the global sea level will rise , which will cause harm to the low - altitude areas .
the center at the university of science and technology , which is located on its website ( nidc . org ) , said that it may have a total of 10,000 people in 2000 and the ice of the 720 million tons of ice , and the ice has been split from january 31 this year , and the ice has been forming several thousand pieces of ice in the weihai sea .
the center also said that the reason why ice - splitting was caused by climate warming in the region .
