chinese engineers sentenced to five years ' imprisonment for illegally obtaining state secrets and offering bribes to chinese - american chinese engineers
( beijing , united states ) beijing 's first intermediate people 's court yesterday ruled that the chinese - american engineer fang fuming was sentenced to five years ' imprisonment and that he had illegally obtained state secrets and a company 's bribes .
this case has caused protests from the united states .
a spokesman for the us embassy in china said that the man will be deported after his term of imprisonment .
the prison term will be adjusted based on his length of imprisonment .
the us embassy had sent a diplomat to listen to the hearing .
the representative of fang fuming 's lawyer said that his party has been imprisoned for two years , but china has not said so long .
the xinhua news agency confirmed the verdict .
it said that from 1995 to 1999 , fang fuming received 35 documents including state secrets , and took bribes of $ 24,000 ( now about $ 450,000 ) from chinese civil servants to assist foreign investors in bidding for china 's electric power projects .
fang fuming was the adviser to the power engineering project of foreign companies in china and other asian countries .
the lawyer of fang fuming said : fang fuming denied offering bribes and indicated that he is the victim of corruption - related chinese power officials .
in the past , fang fuming was a chinese power official and became a us citizen in 1994 .
in the past two years , a number of us citizens and residents have been charged with violating china 's national security law .
fang fuming was detained for a time for tense sino - us relations .
the us government has repeatedly protested china 's method of handling the fangming case , saying that the authorities have been detained by the authorities for a few months and have not tried to go against international norms .
fang fuming 's family said that he was accorded a bad treatment .
his wife and two children are american citizens .
cohen said that fang fuming was detained on 28 february 2000 , but the period of detention put forward by the chinese ministry of foreign affairs was 28 august 2000 .
the chinese navy ship task force 's visit to the united states is also unwilling to confirm whether hu jintao will visit the united states according to his original plan .
beijing , ( xinhua ) the sino - us relations , which were once warming up in the wake of us president bush 's visit to china , were rapidly cooling down , and china confirmed yesterday that this year 's plan for the naval vessel formation to visit the us port and refused to confirm whether state vice president hu jintao will visit the united states in accordance with the original plan .
in reply to a regular reporter 's question , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue said : " according to what i know , the chinese navy fleet is preparing to visit the country according to the plan , and their plans are not included in the us port . "
when a reporter asked on two occasions whether or not hu jintao 's visit to the united states has been affected , she asked to clarify whether or not a reply can be understood earlier as scheduled for hu jintao 's visit to the united states , and zhang qiyue is unwilling to make more comments and is unwilling to confirm it .
zhang qiyue only repeatedly accused the us side of " making a series of things that violate the three sino - us joint communiques in a short period of one month after bush 's visit to china , " and urged the us side to " stop using the taiwan issue to interfere in china 's internal affairs . "
on the other hand , in washington , the united states has ignored the " cold wind " in china 's warning of sino - us relations . on wednesday , the united states has ignored the us decision to allow taiwan defense secretary to attend the " us - taiwan defense summit " in florida .
beijing has repeatedly criticized the united states for issuing a visa to taiwan defense minister tang yao - ming to attend the meeting sponsored by us arms dealers .
at that time , tang yao - ming also met with two senior us officials .
at a regular press conference , state department spokesman bao runshi was questioned by a reporter about china 's complaint against the incident , but he was very clear that he was doing his best to avoid engaging in a war with china .
he said : " after the talks , our position is known to all .
you want to ask me everyday , i am willing to explain everyday , china wants to ask this matter every day , and we are willing to explain it daily . "
he said : " the position has not changed . these are normal contacts between us and taiwanese , and we will continue to do so . "
zhang qiyue also confirmed the report of the russian media yesterday , saying that chinese president jiang zemin had a telephone conversation with russian president putin at the request of russian president putin on the evening of 20 april , and the two sides mainly exchanged views on the issue of mutually beneficial cooperation between china and russia .
both sides held that developing mutually beneficial cooperation between china and russia is in the interests of the two countries and the two peoples .
